.. -*- mode: rst; coding: utf-8 -*-

============================================
Star Traders: A Game of Interstellar Trading
============================================

This directory, `po`, contains translations for text strings used in Star
Traders.  The `GNU Gettext project`__ is used for this purpose.

__ https://www.gnu.org/software/gettext/


Upstream Translation Project
============================

This version of the directory contains files received from the
`Translation Project`__.  These are merged into the master branch as
appropriate.

__ https://www.translationproject.org
